{"tid":1446423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有指大批警員偽裝示威者　疑向防暴警察投擲汽油彈施襲","createTime":"2019-08-11T14:59:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T15:09:21.000Z","uid":114891,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"170f49786177412e687a891b82b8554ed5c7c4de","tid":1446423,"uid":114891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:59:31.000Z","msg":"警務處處長探望燒傷同事<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  警務處處長盧偉聰今日（八月十一日）晚上，到瑪嘉烈醫院探望今日較早前，在尖沙咀警署內執勤時被暴徒投擲汽油彈引致雙腳燒傷的一名同事。對於有同事因為執勤時受到嚴重傷害，處長感到非常難過。<br />\n   <br />\n  對於暴徒罔顧他人安全的非法暴力行為，處長感到非常憤慨，並予以最強烈譴責。針對任何引致他人身體嚴重受傷、甚至威脅生命安全的暴力行為，警隊必定全力追究。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年8月11日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間22時12分<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1bJqYD3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1bJqYD3.png&h=58900fa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w5QkNxq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw5QkNxq.png&h=c20e3bb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67878097_3010172335690785_6507589831055376384_n.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_oc=AQkLTArlp2kpaxXd2RWx0foa2idXsCNSUND8eWNpXlwpIXvoV5Agf6xsl6AlJh1969Q&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=14f7b193a8fa296b74840ccfd6ae366c&amp;oe=5DE22174\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67878097_3010172335690785_6507589831055376384_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26_nc_oc%3DAQkLTArlp2kpaxXd2RWx0foa2idXsCNSUND8eWNpXlwpIXvoV5Agf6xsl6AlJh1969Q%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3D14f7b193a8fa296b74840ccfd6ae366c%26oe%3D5DE22174&h=70f165de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jQ8yn5M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjQ8yn5M.png&h=2c8f4d6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/35JeRY7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F35JeRY7.png&h=f20d1d42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http